<br>
Basically, 16 clerics stood around the platform above Karafym in a big circle.<br>
<br>
The 16 clerics were just barely in healing range of each other, like a long chain.  This is called the cheal chain.  1 warrior then aggroed the 4th warder, and ran backwards while meleeing him around and around the sleeper, as he passed each cleric, he would get a cheal.<br>
<br>
Druids, Paladins, and other worthless classes would get damage shields from mages, then sit in the path of the 4th warder to gain aggro, and do DS damage, with a rez cleric following to re-rez them, this was basically a new passive zerg technique developed specifically for this fight.<br>
<br>
Wizards groups were stationed at each corner, and nuked the 4th warder as he passed, it took over 30 minutes, but in the end the Sleeper did awaken.<br>
<br>
Merloc<br>
<br>
EDIT: This is not really the strategy used by Blood of the Spider, just my little idea after the fact.  Congratulations to Blood of the Spider for doing what no one else could do. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umerloc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Merloc</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0> at: 7/31/01 8:58:05 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucastaa123.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Castaa123</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/31/01 12:23:40 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.neverwhen.com/EQ/castaa/CastaaBust60.jpeg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: WTG Samadhi on freeing The Sleeper!!!!</span><hr size=1> Wow.  Nice strategy.  Who thought that up? <p><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=50949><b><font size="3" color="#cc1313">Castaa</font></b></a>  <a href=http://www.ruis-saille.f2s.com/mbr.html><b><font size="3" color="#009933">&ltRuis Saille&gt</font></a>  <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/bruissaille><b><font size="1" color="#009933">Message Board</font></a></b><BR><b>60 - wizard<BR>Fennin Ro</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uemilsinclair.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Emil Sinclair</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/31/01 8:34:47 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: WTG Samadhi on freeing The Sleeper!!!!</span><hr size=1> HAHA <p><table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" bgcolor="#000000" bordercolorlight="#808080" bordercolo